{"id": 95, "genre": 1000, "title": "长假结束，你惆怅什么？", "description": "虽然明知该来的总会来，但假期总要面临终将结束的命运，瓦们还是流下了痛苦的泪水！以为自己可以度过悠然假期，结果又在“我干了什么？我好像什么都没干啊！”的自我诘问中迎来了工作日的曙光……", "record_count": 1667, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161921Xq9habCl8UEN1PjG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-10-08T07:55:52Z", "questions": [{"id": 96, "title": "长假结束，你惆怅什么？", "content": "长假结束，你惆怅什么？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 832, "content": "我玩得好嗨森啊，可是时光为何如此匆匆！", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618318nPQ7NlUptGaFYs3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 833, "content": "整个假期我被堵在路上，挤在人堆，很痛苦", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161831qlPU9puheXcswRA7.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 834, "content": "我出席了一堆婚礼，心情很复杂", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161831DCXv1Py2R5aiOTWn.JPG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 835, "content": "我的假期都没有上午……我好后悔", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161831gYeZxHJoTRNKShnw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 836, "content": "我以为我会在假期把积攒的活儿都干完呵呵", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161832nCaiXom6xls9YWzQ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 837, "content": "我以为我会在假期好好休息结果呵呵呵呵", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161832syNcAzbG2FHdnRJD.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 838, "content": "假期后调休的班还要上呢好痛苦", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161833rdPyCHZqYGnh370p.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 839, "content": "听说2014的法定假期已经全部结束了嘤嘤嘤", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618339B7MRHhywk5UNSv4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}